header.description: Property.  Standard ROS header contains information  about the frame in which this  contact is specified

position.description: Property.  Position of the contact point

normal.description: Property.  Normal corresponding to the contact point

contact_body_1.description: Property.  Name of the first body that is in contact  This could be a link or a namespace that represents a body

contact_body_2.description: Property.  Name of the second body that is in contact  This could be a link or a namespace that represents a body
